---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="How this site handles data, cookies, and advertising."
	pubDate={new Date('July 17 2026')}
>
	<p>
		This policy covers <strong>ajaycent.com</strong> and its subdomains, including the election
		tracker at elections.ajaycent.com (together, "this site").
	</p>

	<h2>What this site collects</h2>
	<p>
		This site has no user accounts and no forms. It does not ask for, or store, any personal
		information directly. Reading this site does not require giving it any data.
	</p>

	<h2>Hosting</h2>
	<p>
		This site is hosted on Cloudflare. Like most web hosts, Cloudflare processes standard technical
		data (such as IP addresses and request logs) to serve the site and protect it from abuse. See
		the <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a> for
		details.
	</p>

	<h2>Advertising and cookies</h2>
	<p>
		This site may display ads served by Google AdSense. Google and its partners may use cookies
		(including the DoubleClick cookie) to serve ads based on your visits to this and other
		websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising at
		<a href="https://adssettings.google.com">Google Ads Settings</a>, and learn more about how
		Google uses data at
		<a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites"
			>How Google uses information from sites that use its services</a
		>. Visitors in the European Economic Area and the UK are shown a consent message before any
		advertising cookies are set.
	</p>

	<h2>Analytics</h2>
	<p>
		This site does not currently run third-party analytics scripts. If that changes, this policy
		will be updated.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:wizard944@gmail.com">wizard944@gmail.com</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
